tip.text: Rooms are already worn out and basic. However the environment is very peaceful and quiet and is a short walk to the beach.
Hotel is conveniently located near good and decent food such as fried Kway teow, curry noodles and nasi kandar. Rooms size is comfortable and clean. Interior is a pernankan theme.
